    "privileged_info_summary": "The 2024 federal General Schedule pay tables contain verified base pay rates for GS-7 ($41,966 Step 1, $54,557 Step 10), GS-9 ($51,332 Step 1, $66,731 Step 10), and GS-12 ($74,441 Step 1, $96,770 Step 10). Locality adjustments verified from OPM official sources: Washington-Baltimore-Arlington (DCB) at 33.26% locality rate produces Step 1 pay of $55,924 (GS-7), $68,405 (GS-9), $99,200 (GS-12); New York-Newark (NY) at 37.24% locality produces $57,594 (GS-7), $70,448 (GS-9), $102,163 (GS-12); Houston-The Woodlands (HOU) at 34.72% locality produces $56,537 (GS-7), $69,154 (GS-9), $100,287 (GS-12). Task metadata values for locality pay are consistently lower than OPM official values but fall within the stated 10% tolerance threshold. GS-9 Step 10 base pay shows $1 discrepancy (claimed $66,732 vs verified $66,731).",
